*First Playoff [Feb 25, 1953, Estadio Centenario; attendance: 30,000]

2/25/1953; Nacional; 4-2; Penarol; Centenario; Juan Carlos Armental, Washington Rodríguez, Orosmán Rivera Fasoli; 30000
Julio Pérez 24, Jorge Enrico 28, Jorge Enrico 45, Javier Ambrois 44; Oscar Omar Míguez 42, José Emilio Santamaría (og) 46
